      <conclusions>
         <blockContainer class="explanatoryNotes">
            <heading>EXPLANATORY NOTE</heading>
            <block name="comment">(This note is not part of the Regulations)</block>
            <p>These Regulations are made in exercise of the powers conferred by paragraph 1(1) and (3) of schedule 2 of the European Union (Withdrawal) Act 2018. Regulation 2 amends the definition of “wild bird” in section 27(1) of the Wildlife and Countryside Act 1981 to address a deficiency arising from the withdrawal of the United Kingdom from the European Union.</p>
         </blockContainer>
